us largement sur une réflexion philosophique et sociétale.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aInsomnia. 0aSleep deprivation. 0aStress (Physiology). 7aNON-CLASSIFIABLE.2bisacsh1 aLévy,, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102411040uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-84254-233-740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782842542337423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782842542337/original  a978-3-11-102411-0  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2008d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK